node.text: Turned 26 years old today 🎉 (24 if you don’t count COVID years). My friends came to town and got me this American flag speedo as a gift and made me wear it so here’s a pic of me wearing it. Thanks to everyone who has made this year special. Love all of you ❤️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Kade Speiser on July 09, 2021 tagging @mackenziealtig, @followgustavo, and @montchalet. May be an image of mountain.

node.text: Heading home from what I think may have been the most incredible trip overseas that I’ve ever taken. The highlight being my time spent in the Dolomites at @montchalet . Everything about it was perfect, the hotel is unlike anything I’ve ever experienced and the landscape doesn’t even feel real. I’m still having a hard time wrapping my head around the beauty we were immersed in. Thank you so much for having us ❤️
